com.smartnsoft.droid4me.analytics

Annotation Type AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsTagLoggerAnnotation


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public static @interface AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsTagLoggerAnnotation
    An annotation which enables to express that an entity, usually an Activity or a Fragment, wants to report analytics usage.

    Use this annotation, when the entity tag is known at compile tag.

    See Also:
    AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsTagLogger, AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsTagLoggerAnnotation

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String tag 

    • Element Detail

      • tag

        public abstract java.lang.String tag
        Returns:
        the tag that will be used when reporting some usage information about the underlying entity ; it may return null
